'\x3c!-- IEBinaryToArray_ByteStr --\x3e
Function IEBinaryToArray_ByteStr(Binary)
   IEBinaryToArray_ByteStr \x3d CStr(Binary)
End Function
Function IEBinaryToArray_ByteStr_Last(Binary)
   Dim lastIndex
   lastIndex \x3d LenB(Binary)
   if lastIndex mod 2 Then
       IEBinaryToArray_ByteStr_Last \x3d Chr( AscB( MidB( Binary, lastIndex, 1 ) ) )
   Else
       IEBinaryToArray_ByteStr_Last \x3d ""
   End If
End Function
'
